+#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
+#
+#  Makefile :             Makefile for compiling CImg examples
+#
+#  Author :               David Tschumperlé
+#
+#  Institution :          ODYSSEE, INRIA Sophia Antipolis.
+#
+#  Contact :              David.Tschumperle@sophia.inria.fr
+#
+#  Date :                 Project started november 1999.
